						<summary>

						<p>Slab lying in front of the Hazrat Teg Burhanuddin Dargah-(2).</p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">1310 A.D.</hi></p>						

						<p>This slab contains two records. The first one is in Nagari Script and Sanskrit language. This portion of the record is very much damaged. It records a <hi rend="italic">sarvamānya</hi> grant [of land] by Gangi-dēva-rāṇeya. Probably it belongs to the same date as engraved in the previous record, <hi rend="italic">viz.,</hi> 1310 A.D.</p>						

						</summary>
